%vlocity_namespace%__PropertySet__c.label: Participation Requirement
%vlocity_namespace%__PropertySet__c.text:
Participation Requirement

Basic Life, Basic Accidental Death & Dismemberment, Short Term Disability: 100%textNode% participation required on non-contributory plans and 75%textNode% participation required on contributory plans.

Long Term Disability: 100%textNode% participation required on all non-contributory plans. 100%textNode% participation required for contributory plans of two or three eligible employees. 75%textNode% participation required on contributory plans with four or more eligible employees.
Basic Dependent Life: 100%textNode% participation required on non-contributory plans.
Optional Supplemental/Voluntary Life/Accidental Death & Dismemberment: The greater of five enrolled employees or 20%textNode% participation required.
Voluntary Short Term Disability and Voluntary Long Term Disability: The greater of 10 enrolled employees or 20%textNode% participation required.
